description: Deedle implements an efficient and robust frame and series data structures for manipulating with structured data. It supports handling of missing values, aggregations, grouping, joining, statistical functions and more. For frames and series with ordered indices (such as time series), automatic alignment is also available.  This package installs the core Deedle package, NetOffice.Excel, and a Deedle extension which makes it possible to send Deedle Frames to Excel.
